This table lists words from the group **origin** or **source**:

| **Hebrew Word** | **Transcription** | **Meaning** | **Context/Usage** |  
|---------------|----------------|------------|-----------------|  
| **שׁוֹרֶשׁ** | *Shoresh* | Root (literal, linguistic, figurative) | Plants, Hebrew grammar, ancestry |  
| **מָקוֹר** | *Makor* | Source, origin | Information, ideas, water sources |  
| **מוֹצָא** | *Motza* | Place of origin, exit | Geography, ethnicity, direction |  
